texts.text:
Legacy Console Edition, the version of Minecraft developed by 4J Studios for the following consoles:
Xbox 360 Edition
Xbox One Edition
PlayStation 3 Edition
PlayStation 4 Edition
PlayStation Vita Edition
Wii U Edition
Nintendo Switch Edition
Bedrock Edition, the version of Minecraft that supports crossplay on Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PlayStation 4.
New Nintendo 3DS Edition, the version of Minecraft for the New Nintendo 3DS, the New Nintendo 3DS XL, and the New Nintendo 2DS XL.
